Sentencas: Anodes for Solid Oxide Fuel Cells (SOFCs) that are capable of directly using hydrocarbon fuels without external reforming have been of great interest in the recent years.
Titulo: Improvement of multi-layer anode for direct ethanol Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: We have fabricated a two-layer structure containing a Cu-CeO2 catalyst layer by tape casting and screen printing technology.
Titulo: Improvement of multi-layer anode for direct ethanol Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: The interface combination between the Cu-CeO2 catalyst layer and the Ni-YSZ-supported anode issues importantly for the stability of the anode structure.
Titulo: Improvement of multi-layer anode for direct ethanol Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: In this paper, a Ni-CeO2 interlayer was added between these two layers to improve the long-term stability of the multi-layer anode.
Titulo: Improvement of multi-layer anode for direct ethanol Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Meanwhile, the exit gas of the single cell was also analyzed by a gas chromatographer (GC) to determine the reaction mechanism of the ethanol fuel in the anode.
Titulo: Improvement of multi-layer anode for direct ethanol Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
